functions.name: test_tmpconfigdir_warning
functions.docstring: Test that a warning is emitted if a temporary configdir must be used.

functions.name: test_use_doc_standard_backends
functions.docstring:
Test that the standard backends mentioned in the docstring of
matplotlib.use() are the same as in matplotlib.rcsetup.

functions.name: test_importable_with__OO
functions.docstring:
When using -OO or export PYTHONOPTIMIZE=2, docstrings are discarded,
this simple test may prevent something like issue #17970.

functions.name: test_get_executable_info_timeout
functions.docstring:
Test that _get_executable_info raises ExecutableNotFoundError if the
command times out.
